.5<br />\n我想dvd+3.5+2.5.......</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來可以唔裝80mm fan<br />\n就有多個位<br />\n<br />\n不過唔裝既話散熱ok吧？</blockquote><br />\n又係魚與熊掌問題<br />\n你預係夏天打機有機會overheat</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nc10既話有fd用緊，用緊張公版卡同埋無裝case fan/原裝cpu fan 之前過疑似熱自動熄左</blockquote><br />\nCPU熱氣撞顯示卡背板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nC10用家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncpu fan用 NH-D9L"},{"pid":"2c0546cef77b9a19442ca9747611ec88e929f2ec","tid":188094,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T21:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/012400_58c78d44a71a9d0dad203e8d05f00c61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F012400_58c78d44a71a9d0dad203e8d05f00c61.jpg&h=5b82ad61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面講過啦 今次俾埋圖你<br />\n火牛用neoeco2 450/550啦</blockquote><br />\n此外在 5.25 吋磁碟槽位置可安裝光碟機，此時內部仍可安裝 1 個 3.5 吋硬碟或 1 個 2.5 吋硬碟/SSD；<br />\n<br />\n只能dvd+3.5 或 dvd+2.5<br />\n我想dvd+3.5+2.5.......</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來可以唔裝80mm fan<br />\n就有多個位<br />\n<br />\n不過唔裝既話散熱ok吧？</blockquote><br />\n又係魚與熊掌問題<br />\n你預係夏天打機有機會overheat</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nc10既話有fd用緊，用緊張公版卡同埋無裝case fan/原裝cpu fan 之前過疑似熱自動熄左</blockquote><br />\nCPU熱氣撞顯示卡背板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa